1
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:35,009
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:39,450
[1998]

3
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:36,560
Xiaolan,

4
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,350
look what I made.

5
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:40,680
Ribs, your favorite.

6
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:42,210
Xiaolan,

7
00:01:42,740 --> 00:01:44,740
wash your hands and get ready to eat.

8
00:02:08,590 --> 00:02:09,120
Xiaolan!

9
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,090
Xiaolan!

10
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,800
Why did you come here instead of

11
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,200
going home after school?

12
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:17,000
Are you trying to scare me to death?

13
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:18,400
I'm sorry, Auntie.

14
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:21,030
I miss Mom and Dad.

15
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,280
Silly child.

16
00:02:28,430 --> 00:02:30,120
Your parents are gone,

17
00:02:30,910 --> 00:02:33,110
but you still have your own life to live.

18
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:34,710
You need to

19
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:37,220
live your life well, step by step.

20
00:02:37,470 --> 00:02:38,280
Understand?

21
00:02:45,170 --> 00:02:47,740
[Episode 8: Every Step in Life]

22
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,200
They are here!

23
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:25,829
Silly boy!

24
00:03:27,630 --> 00:03:28,120
Mom.

25
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,590
Mom!

26
00:03:30,190 --> 00:03:31,590
Xiaolan! Xiaolan!

27
00:03:43,310 --> 00:03:45,030
Everyone, quiet down please!

28
00:03:47,100 --> 00:03:48,360
[Warm congratulations to Xia Xiaolan,
a villager from Qijing Village,]

29
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:48,710
Let me say a few words.

30
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,620
[for becoming the top scorer in the
college entrance exam in Yunan Province]

31
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:51,190
I'm very happy today.

32
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:53,190
Our village has never had

33
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,840
a top scorer before.

34
00:03:55,190 --> 00:03:57,630
But today, Xiaolan did it.

35
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,750
Aren't we all happy?

36
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:02,080
Yes!

37
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:05,140
And Chen Qing did well too.

38
00:04:05,190 --> 00:04:06,360
With over 500 points,

39
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:08,430
he can also get into
a university in Jingcheng.

40
00:04:08,430 --> 00:04:09,960
Xiaolan is our "top scholar,"

41
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:10,750
and Chen Qing

42
00:04:10,910 --> 00:04:12,520
is at least an "imperial scholar," right?

43
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,630
Yes!

44
00:04:13,650 --> 00:04:14,340
Yes!

45
00:04:15,750 --> 00:04:16,160
Yes!

46
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,450
And I want to thank Chief

47
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,870
for helping us
move our household registration back.

48
00:04:20,870 --> 00:04:22,120
And I want to thank

49
00:04:22,190 --> 00:04:23,830
all the uncles and aunties in the village

50
00:04:23,830 --> 00:04:25,340
for taking care of us.

51
00:04:25,430 --> 00:04:26,600
Thank you.

52
00:04:26,630 --> 00:04:27,240
Thank you.

53
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,120
Such a good kid.

54
00:04:28,870 --> 00:04:30,270
Chen Qing and Xiaolan

55
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:32,280
are the pride of our village.

56
00:04:32,750 --> 00:04:34,800
The slogan on this wall says it well:

57
00:04:35,070 --> 00:04:37,000
"Knowledge can change your life."

58
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:38,290
I hope you all

59
00:04:38,510 --> 00:04:39,920
learn from them,

60
00:04:40,159 --> 00:04:41,310
study hard

61
00:04:41,659 --> 00:04:42,750
and get into universities—

62
00:04:42,750 --> 00:04:44,000
good universities!

63
00:04:44,750 --> 00:04:45,870
All parents

64
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,920
should support their children.

65
00:04:48,070 --> 00:04:49,190
Both boys and girls

66
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,780
should be allowed to go to school

67
00:04:50,780 --> 00:04:51,390
and study.

68
00:04:51,630 --> 00:04:53,230
If your family has any difficulties,

69
00:04:53,230 --> 00:04:54,630
please speak up.

70
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:57,110
The village will help.

71
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:59,310
Bravo!

72
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:01,040
Xiaolan is amazing.

73
00:05:01,630 --> 00:05:02,720
These children...

74
00:05:02,830 --> 00:05:04,680
have been through so much.

75
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:05,650
Alright now.

76
00:05:05,870 --> 00:05:07,160
On such a happy day,

77
00:05:07,430 --> 00:05:08,950
let's not shed tears.

78
00:05:09,310 --> 00:05:10,750
I am just happy.

79
00:05:10,950 --> 00:05:11,630
Yes, yes.

80
00:05:11,950 --> 00:05:13,070
Everyone,

81
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:14,630
come to our house for drinks tonight!

82
00:05:14,630 --> 00:05:16,720
Great!

83
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,190
Everyone come!

84
00:05:30,700 --> 00:05:31,800
Although you didn't pass this year,

85
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,000
you'll definitely get in next year.

86
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:33,930
I had a good time.

87
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,270
Study hard, okay?

88
00:05:36,270 --> 00:05:37,040
Be careful on the way home.

89
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:39,300
Learn from Xiaolan and get into college.

90
00:05:39,510 --> 00:05:40,750
Uncle Yong, don't worry!

91
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:42,950
I'll definitely work harder next year.

92
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:45,159
Okay. Thank you.

93
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,720
What a happy day.

94
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,159
Fen,

95
00:05:47,390 --> 00:05:47,950
Xiaolan.

96
00:05:48,070 --> 00:05:49,240
Get some rest early.

97
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:49,920
Okay.

98
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:51,600
Fen, don't bother cleaning up today.

99
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,530
It's too tiring.

100
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,159
Get some rest early.

101
00:05:53,159 --> 00:05:54,260
Your brother is drunk.

102
00:05:54,260 --> 00:05:55,300
Who's drunk?

103
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:57,040
I can walk in a straight line.

104
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,770
That's enough. Get inside now.

105
00:06:00,950 --> 00:06:01,560
Xiaolan.

106
00:06:02,430 --> 00:06:03,270
Well...

107
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,760
I need to tell you something.

108
00:06:05,870 --> 00:06:06,920
Don't be mad.

109
00:06:08,190 --> 00:06:09,190
On the day

110
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:11,000
Xia Dajun got the divorce certificate,

111
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:11,860
he disappeared

112
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:14,680
and there's been no word from him since.

113
00:06:16,270 --> 00:06:16,750
Mom,

114
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:17,950
I'm not mad.

115
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:19,430
I know

116
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:21,160
you're not being foolish

117
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,630
and thinking about the Xia family

118
00:06:22,630 --> 00:06:24,120
or holding onto Xia Dajun.

119
00:06:25,070 --> 00:06:26,270
You're just too kind.

120
00:06:27,190 --> 00:06:28,270
Usually, you even show concern

121
00:06:28,270 --> 00:06:29,070
for strangers

122
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,700
when they suffer a little—

123
00:06:30,950 --> 00:06:31,830
let alone

124
00:06:32,270 --> 00:06:32,950
your ex‑husband,

125
00:06:32,950 --> 00:06:35,010
whom you lived with for so many years.

126
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:37,510
I just wanted to tell him

127
00:06:38,070 --> 00:06:40,200
that you got into Huaqing University.

128
00:06:40,390 --> 00:06:41,450
I didn't expect...

129
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:44,870
the Xia family to be in such chaos now.

130
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:46,800
I guess this is karma.

131
00:06:48,159 --> 00:06:49,270
Alright, stop thinking about it anymore.

132
00:06:49,270 --> 00:06:50,070
Let's go home.

133
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:50,650
Xiaolan!

134
00:06:51,430 --> 00:06:51,960
Xiaolan!

135
00:06:52,070 --> 00:06:53,270
You have a phone call!

136
00:06:53,570 --> 00:06:54,270
It's at the village committee.

137
00:06:54,270 --> 00:06:54,720
Go now.

138
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:55,120
Okay.

139
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:56,300
Thank you, Auntie.

140
00:06:56,710 --> 00:06:57,430
This child...

141
00:06:57,430 --> 00:06:58,360
Such a good girl.

142
00:06:59,159 --> 00:06:59,760
Mrs. Chen,

143
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:01,510
who called her?

144
00:07:02,950 --> 00:07:04,810
I was in such a hurry to come get her

145
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,130
that I forgot to ask.

146
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,480
How did these two kids

147
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,430
turn out to be so outstanding?

148
00:07:09,430 --> 00:07:11,490
Yes, yes. Chen Qing is excellent too.

149
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:14,480
Hello?

150
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:15,520
Congratulations,

151
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:16,430
Xia Xiaolan,

152
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:19,070
for becoming
the top science student in Yunan.

153
00:07:19,070 --> 00:07:19,800
Thank you.

154
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,190
How did you do?

155
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:24,270
I can't compare myself

156
00:07:24,270 --> 00:07:26,070
with the provincial top scorer,

157
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:26,800
but...

158
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:27,720
I should be able

159
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:29,250
to get into Huaqing as well.

160
00:07:29,430 --> 00:07:31,030
I can be your schoolmate now.

161
00:07:32,830 --> 00:07:33,510
Xiaolan,

162
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:35,440
what gift do you want?

163
00:07:35,980 --> 00:07:37,570
My college entrance exam score

164
00:07:37,570 --> 00:07:38,970
is already the best gift.

165
00:07:40,390 --> 00:07:42,320
I'm talking about a birthday gift.

166
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:43,720
What?

167
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:44,920
Don't tell me you're so happy

168
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,750
that you've forgotten your own birthday.

169
00:07:46,750 --> 00:07:47,630
My birthday?

170
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,510
This is your first birthday

171
00:07:49,510 --> 00:07:50,950
since we've known each other.

172
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:51,870
I wanted

173
00:07:51,870 --> 00:07:53,130
to give you a surprise,

174
00:07:53,390 --> 00:07:54,390
but then I thought

175
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,480
it would be better to give you something

176
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:57,340
you truly like.

177
00:07:57,950 --> 00:07:58,950
Anything is fine,

178
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:00,360
as long as
you don't pack yourself in a box

179
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,870
and send yourself over.

180
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:04,920
That's an option?

181
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:05,920
Just kidding.

182
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:07,250
Don't actually do that.

183
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,410
Maybe I will.

184
00:08:08,950 --> 00:08:10,750
Your gift will arrive next week.

185
00:08:10,830 --> 00:08:11,190
Okay.

186
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,800
See you next week.

187
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,720
See you next week?

188
00:08:21,510 --> 00:08:22,920
Can you finally tell me

189
00:08:23,830 --> 00:08:25,680
why you've been going to Yunan?

190
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,240
Director Guan, you've probably wanted

191
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,390
to ask this for a long time, right?

192
00:08:30,390 --> 00:08:31,510
You must be dying to know.

193
00:08:31,510 --> 00:08:32,630
Of course.

194
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:35,400
Didn't I want you
to focus on the college entrance exam?

195
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:36,510
Now that the exam is over

196
00:08:36,510 --> 00:08:37,480
and the celebration's done,

197
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,600
don't you think

198
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:40,000
you owe your mom a report?

199
00:08:40,390 --> 00:08:40,919
Alright.

200
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,440
Well then, Director Guan,

201
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,840
I'll give you the report.

202
00:08:44,820 --> 00:08:47,350
Her name is Xia Xiaolan.

203
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:50,550
She's from Qijing Village, Yunan Province.

204
00:08:50,550 --> 00:08:52,270
She took the college entrance exam
with me this year

205
00:08:52,270 --> 00:08:54,730
and became
the top science student in Yunan.

206
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,550
She's been admitted to Huaqing University,

207
00:08:57,550 --> 00:08:58,870
majoring in Architecture,

208
00:08:58,870 --> 00:09:00,600
and will soon be my schoolmate.

209
00:09:02,190 --> 00:09:03,340
The English study tips

210
00:09:03,340 --> 00:09:04,550
posted on the wall

211
00:09:04,550 --> 00:09:05,840
in front of your desk...

212
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,320
they're hers, right?

213
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,380
Yes, that's right.

214
00:09:08,510 --> 00:09:09,630
If she hadn't helped me improve my English

215
00:09:09,630 --> 00:09:10,600
by over 30 points,

216
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,660
I might not have been admitted at all.

217
00:09:13,630 --> 00:09:15,430
She, a kid from the countryside,

218
00:09:16,630 --> 00:09:19,150
became the top science student
in her province?

219
00:09:19,150 --> 00:09:20,190
First in Yunan,

220
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,700
and 3rd in the country.

221
00:09:22,870 --> 00:09:23,600
Impressive.

222
00:09:24,270 --> 00:09:26,120
Actually, I made up my mind

223
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,120
to repeat a year

224
00:09:27,500 --> 00:09:29,230
because of her encouragement.

225
00:09:29,390 --> 00:09:29,960
I admit

226
00:09:30,580 --> 00:09:32,350
I have feelings for her.

227
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,890
And I expressed my feelings to her.

228
00:09:35,150 --> 00:09:35,870
But...

229
00:09:36,030 --> 00:09:37,090
she turned me down.

230
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:39,880
I really admire her.

231
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,480
She didn't say yes

232
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:42,790
because of my background.

233
00:09:42,790 --> 00:09:44,200
Instead, she chose to rely on herself—

234
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,260
and she succeeded.

235
00:09:46,150 --> 00:09:48,080
So I have to keep working hard

236
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:49,140
to be worthy of her.

237
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,840
How are you not worthy of her?

238
00:09:52,380 --> 00:09:53,960
Let's not even mention you were born
into the Zhou family.

239
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:54,480
Right?

240
00:09:54,870 --> 00:09:56,270
You got into Huaqing

241
00:09:56,270 --> 00:09:57,440
on your own ability.

242
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:59,120
The top scorer

243
00:09:59,390 --> 00:10:01,240
only beat you by a few points.

244
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,080
How did my son end up

245
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,510
losing confidence because of that?
Seriously.

246
00:10:03,510 --> 00:10:04,240
Mom.

247
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:06,960
It's precisely because
I was born into the Zhou family

248
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:08,550
that I feel I'm not worthy of her.

249
00:10:08,550 --> 00:10:09,080
Look,

250
00:10:09,550 --> 00:10:11,440
our family gave me such good conditions,

251
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:11,910
so my starting point

252
00:10:11,910 --> 00:10:13,480
was higher than many people's.

253
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:14,540
But what about her?

254
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:16,320
She was born in the countryside,

255
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:17,230
with tough

256
00:10:17,270 --> 00:10:18,470
material conditions

257
00:10:18,510 --> 00:10:20,040
and learning environment.

258
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,200
And in her family,

259
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,270
there are...

260
00:10:23,510 --> 00:10:24,040
In short,

261
00:10:24,640 --> 00:10:26,170
she must've put in hundreds

262
00:10:26,180 --> 00:10:27,720
or thousands of times more effort

263
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:28,920
than I did to get here.

264
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:30,080
So she's...

265
00:10:30,750 --> 00:10:31,630
smarter...

266
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:33,930
and braver than me.

267
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:37,750
Do you know how happy I am

268
00:10:37,750 --> 00:10:39,030
to hear you say that?

269
00:10:40,580 --> 00:10:41,230
Looks like

270
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,800
you're serious about this girl.

271
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,730
So your birthday is in July.

272
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,960
I wonder if you're satisfied

273
00:11:09,470 --> 00:11:11,470
with the time we've spent together.

274
00:11:12,910 --> 00:11:14,600
I increasingly want

275
00:11:15,510 --> 00:11:17,240
to carry both our courage

276
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,000
and dreams

277
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:20,000
and see

278
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:21,600
how far I can go.

279
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:31,690
Be careful, be careful.

280
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:33,390
Take a break if you're tired. Be careful.

281
00:11:33,390 --> 00:11:34,480
Don't force yourself.

282
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:35,360
Be careful. Be careful.

283
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:36,910
Stop hanging onto me.

284
00:11:37,150 --> 00:11:38,120
You might as well help me

285
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:38,910
carry the TV.

286
00:11:38,910 --> 00:11:40,240
Alright. I'll carry both you and the TV.

287
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,120
Come on. Hurry.

288
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:41,670
Careful.

289
00:11:41,670 --> 00:11:42,120
Alright. Alright.

290
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:43,000
Easy, easy, easy.

291
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:44,080
Careful now.

292
00:11:45,550 --> 00:11:46,680
-Okay.
-Be careful.

293
00:11:46,910 --> 00:11:47,550
Come on, straighten it.

294
00:11:47,550 --> 00:11:48,440
Turn it around.

295
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:49,700
Straighten it.

296
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:50,900
Take a look.

297
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:51,870
Dayong.

298
00:11:52,390 --> 00:11:52,790
Thanks for your hard work.

299
00:11:52,790 --> 00:11:53,960
Your relative is here.

300
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:55,620
He's waiting at the entrance.

301
00:11:57,090 --> 00:11:58,140
I'll go check.

302
00:11:58,480 --> 00:11:59,010
Go ahead.

303
00:12:00,140 --> 00:12:01,410
Listen,

304
00:12:01,630 --> 00:12:03,560
your job is just to keep an eye on it.

305
00:12:03,630 --> 00:12:05,160
Don't let anyone get close.

306
00:12:14,630 --> 00:12:15,960
What are you looking at?

307
00:12:17,670 --> 00:12:18,080
Uncle.

308
00:12:18,910 --> 00:12:19,970
Don't call me that.

309
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:23,550
How long have you been here?

310
00:12:23,550 --> 00:12:24,880
J-just arrived, Uncle.

311
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:27,240
Just arrived?

312
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:32,910
Mr. Zhou.

313
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:36,240
Did you get into college?

314
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:37,000
I did.

315
00:12:37,550 --> 00:12:39,010
Huaqing, majoring in Law.

316
00:12:40,630 --> 00:12:42,030
You got into Huaqing too?

317
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:45,320
That's impressive! Amazing!

318
00:12:47,390 --> 00:12:48,240
Our Xiaolan

319
00:12:48,630 --> 00:12:50,510
is Yunan's top scorer!

320
00:12:51,020 --> 00:12:52,080
She even went on TV

321
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,150
for an interview.

322
00:12:53,350 --> 00:12:54,880
We've already set up the TV.

323
00:12:55,030 --> 00:12:56,120
The whole village is coming tonight

324
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:58,000
to watch her interview.

325
00:12:58,170 --> 00:12:59,510
You've arrived just in time.

326
00:12:59,510 --> 00:13:00,970
Join us and learn from her.

327
00:13:01,390 --> 00:13:01,840
Okay.

328
00:13:04,030 --> 00:13:05,430
What's that in your hand?

329
00:13:06,440 --> 00:13:07,000
This...

330
00:13:07,150 --> 00:13:08,880
is a birthday cake for Xiaolan.

331
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:14,510
Their shop

332
00:13:14,510 --> 00:13:15,440
is closing soon,

333
00:13:16,150 --> 00:13:17,480
and she'll be back then.

334
00:13:18,270 --> 00:13:19,270
Thank you, Uncle.

335
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:21,220
Stop calling me Uncle.

336
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:26,270
Alright.

337
00:13:26,910 --> 00:13:27,440
It's lit.

338
00:13:29,750 --> 00:13:32,240
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

339
00:13:29,810 --> 00:13:30,500
Ready—

340
00:13:32,680 --> 00:13:35,390
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

341
00:13:35,750 --> 00:13:38,870
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

342
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:42,000
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

343
00:13:49,630 --> 00:13:50,870
I hope everyone I love

344
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:52,320
can be happy.

345
00:13:57,910 --> 00:13:58,840
Happy birthday.

346
00:13:58,840 --> 00:14:00,510
-Happy birthday.
-Happy birthday.

347
00:14:00,510 --> 00:14:01,960
Can we eat the cake now?

348
00:14:02,150 --> 00:14:04,440
This cake from the city is so pretty!

349
00:14:04,630 --> 00:14:05,670
If you behave well,

350
00:14:05,670 --> 00:14:07,670
I'll buy you one next time
I go to the city.

351
00:14:07,670 --> 00:14:08,870
Xiaolan, ignore him.

352
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:10,960
Whatever's next? Please continue.

353
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:13,670
The next thing on the agenda is...

354
00:14:15,270 --> 00:14:16,230
eating cake!

355
00:14:17,870 --> 00:14:18,320
Here.

356
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:31,870
Let's give the biggest piece

357
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:32,810
to Tao!

358
00:14:33,240 --> 00:14:34,200
Come on. What should you say?

359
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:35,320
Thank you, Xiaolan!

360
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:36,630
Happy birthday, Xiaolan.

361
00:14:36,630 --> 00:14:37,960
May you live a long life!

362
00:14:38,390 --> 00:14:40,050
And I hope you grow up healthy!

363
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:47,870
This piece

364
00:14:48,510 --> 00:14:49,370
is for you, Mom.

365
00:14:50,360 --> 00:14:52,240
Mom, you gave birth to me and raised me.

366
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:53,840
Thank you for your hard work.

367
00:14:54,550 --> 00:14:55,750
It wasn't hard for me.

368
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:57,080
Eat up.

369
00:15:06,870 --> 00:15:07,390
Uncle.

370
00:15:07,390 --> 00:15:07,960
Alright.

371
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:08,870
Auntie.

372
00:15:11,750 --> 00:15:13,210
Thank you for taking us in.

373
00:15:14,150 --> 00:15:15,360
This place

374
00:15:15,750 --> 00:15:16,670
is not just a shelter

375
00:15:16,670 --> 00:15:18,270
from the wind and rain for me.

376
00:15:19,510 --> 00:15:20,390
It's my home.

377
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:22,750
Xiaolan,

378
00:15:23,630 --> 00:15:24,690
what you're saying

379
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:26,150
is making me cry.

380
00:15:26,150 --> 00:15:26,550
Yes.

381
00:15:26,550 --> 00:15:28,550
Family doesn't need to be so formal.

382
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:32,000
Eat up.

383
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:42,870
This piece is for you, Zhou Cheng.

384
00:15:42,870 --> 00:15:43,470
Thank you.

385
00:15:44,240 --> 00:15:44,900
Uncle Yong.

386
00:15:45,790 --> 00:15:46,650
Go watch the TV.

387
00:15:46,670 --> 00:15:48,790
Xiaolan's interview is about to start.

388
00:15:48,790 --> 00:15:49,840
Let's go, hurry!

389
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:50,360
Let's go!

390
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:51,080
Let's go over there!

391
00:15:51,080 --> 00:15:52,000
Or we'll miss it.

392
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:52,440
Xiaolan...

393
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:53,150
Coming!

394
00:15:53,390 --> 00:15:53,790
Hurry!

395
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:17,240
In this year's college entrance exam,

396
00:16:17,240 --> 00:16:18,080
Xia Xiaolan
from Anqing County No.1 High School

397
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:19,170
achieved

398
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:20,960
the top science score in Yunan Province

399
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:22,810
with 616 points.

400
00:16:22,960 --> 00:16:24,000
We rushed over

401
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,630
to interview her on the spot.

402
00:16:26,840 --> 00:16:28,440
First, let's congratulate Xia

403
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:29,790
on this outstanding achievement.

404
00:16:29,790 --> 00:16:30,920
Isn't that Xiaolan?

405
00:16:32,840 --> 00:16:33,510
Xia.

406
00:16:34,150 --> 00:16:34,790
So pretty!

407
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:36,150
Xiaolan!

408
00:16:36,870 --> 00:16:37,360
Mom!

409
00:16:37,390 --> 00:16:39,150
Xiaolan is on TV!

410
00:16:39,170 --> 00:16:40,570
Yes, there she is.

411
00:16:41,030 --> 00:16:42,030
Study hard,

412
00:16:42,080 --> 00:16:44,000
and you can be on TV when you grow up.

413
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,070
Quiet, everyone.

414
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:46,120
Please be quiet.

415
00:16:46,120 --> 00:16:47,360
I can't hear Xiaolan.

416
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:48,370
Please be quiet.

417
00:16:49,670 --> 00:16:51,670
I want to thank my teachers
for their guidance

418
00:16:51,670 --> 00:16:53,530
and my classmates for their help.

419
00:16:53,840 --> 00:16:55,240
My achievement today

420
00:16:55,510 --> 00:16:57,040
didn't come out of nowhere.

421
00:16:57,050 --> 00:16:57,850
Without them,

422
00:16:57,870 --> 00:16:59,400
I wouldn't be who I am today.

423
00:16:59,720 --> 00:17:01,750
How thoughtful this kid is!

424
00:17:01,750 --> 00:17:02,270
Right?

425
00:17:02,630 --> 00:17:03,790
Good girl!

426
00:17:04,730 --> 00:17:05,410
Xia,

427
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:06,920
why is your hand in a cast?

428
00:17:06,940 --> 00:17:08,069
Did you get injured?

429
00:17:08,680 --> 00:17:09,069
Yes.

430
00:17:09,310 --> 00:17:11,109
I got injured
before the college entrance exam,

431
00:17:11,109 --> 00:17:12,310
so I had to wear a cast.

432
00:17:12,829 --> 00:17:14,200
Because of that,

433
00:17:14,510 --> 00:17:16,640
my hand movement was limited,

434
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:18,550
and I might not have done so well

435
00:17:18,550 --> 00:17:20,609
on some of the open-ended questions.

436
00:17:37,000 --> 00:17:38,440
Change the channel.

437
00:17:40,360 --> 00:17:42,240
How did you get injured before the exam?

438
00:17:42,240 --> 00:17:43,650
Was it an accident?

439
00:17:48,790 --> 00:17:50,720
Someone stepped on my wrist.

440
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:53,600
I don't know if it counts as an accident.

441
00:18:01,880 --> 00:18:04,010
But fortunately, it didn't affect me.

442
00:18:04,110 --> 00:18:05,830
I also want to use this experience

443
00:18:05,830 --> 00:18:07,360
to tell everyone one thing:

444
00:18:08,480 --> 00:18:09,510
life

445
00:18:09,510 --> 00:18:11,160
is full of unexpected events.

446
00:18:11,160 --> 00:18:12,090
Don't be afraid,

447
00:18:12,240 --> 00:18:13,500
and don't shrink back.

448
00:18:13,550 --> 00:18:14,480
No matter when,

449
00:18:14,880 --> 00:18:16,720
we should always face problems bravely

450
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:17,580
and solve them.

451
00:18:18,750 --> 00:18:19,920
Well said!

452
00:18:20,550 --> 00:18:21,350
Bravo!

453
00:18:21,550 --> 00:18:22,400
Bravo!

454
00:18:22,830 --> 00:18:23,440
This kid

455
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:25,300
is truly the pride of our village!

456
00:18:44,720 --> 00:18:45,350
Xiaolan,

457
00:18:45,430 --> 00:18:46,640
you did so well on TV

458
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:47,450
just now.

459
00:18:47,480 --> 00:18:48,160
Thank you.

460
00:19:03,750 --> 00:19:04,510
Xiaolan.

461
00:19:05,550 --> 00:19:06,440
So what are you

462
00:19:07,350 --> 00:19:08,480
planning to do next?

463
00:19:10,270 --> 00:19:10,870
I'll wait.

464
00:19:12,440 --> 00:19:14,640
The stone has been thrown into the pond,

465
00:19:15,000 --> 00:19:16,760
and the ripples need some time

466
00:19:16,790 --> 00:19:18,000
to reach the shore.

467
00:19:21,720 --> 00:19:23,640
So the words you didn't finish just now...

468
00:19:23,640 --> 00:19:25,970
someone is waiting for you to finish them.

469
00:19:29,480 --> 00:19:30,140
Zhou Cheng.

470
00:19:32,830 --> 00:19:34,640
What I was going to say is...

471
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:38,840
thank you.

472
00:19:41,830 --> 00:19:42,430
That's it?

473
00:19:49,880 --> 00:19:51,540
You always say thank you to me,

474
00:19:52,440 --> 00:19:53,240
but actually,

475
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:57,050
the one you should thank most is yourself.

476
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:58,680
Because it's thanks to you,

477
00:19:58,680 --> 00:19:59,410
who are smart

478
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:00,680
and brave,

479
00:20:01,960 --> 00:20:03,420
that those of us around you

480
00:20:04,070 --> 00:20:05,130
can become better.

481
00:20:06,640 --> 00:20:07,310
Actually,

482
00:20:08,160 --> 00:20:10,360
these past few days, I've been thinking

483
00:20:10,720 --> 00:20:12,250
about what gift to give you—

484
00:20:12,790 --> 00:20:13,550
a watch?

485
00:20:14,350 --> 00:20:15,350
Or maybe jewelry?

486
00:20:16,070 --> 00:20:17,470
No matter how expensive,

487
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:20,080
it still felt like something was missing.

488
00:20:20,790 --> 00:20:21,510
So,

489
00:20:27,790 --> 00:20:28,920
I'm giving you this.

490
00:20:38,750 --> 00:20:39,240
I know

491
00:20:40,550 --> 00:20:41,350
you'll have

492
00:20:41,830 --> 00:20:43,160
an extraordinary life,

493
00:20:44,270 --> 00:20:45,130
and your future

494
00:20:45,590 --> 00:20:46,680
will certainly

495
00:20:46,680 --> 00:20:48,340
shine even brighter than now.

496
00:20:49,720 --> 00:20:50,980
Let this accompany you

497
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:53,440
as you write your brilliant life story.

498
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:22,830
This is the first real victory I've had

499
00:21:22,830 --> 00:21:24,350
since coming here,

500
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:27,600
and the first time
I've truly freed myself.

501
00:21:28,480 --> 00:21:30,200
I hope my future life

502
00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:32,740
can shine as brightly as tonight.

503
00:21:37,440 --> 00:21:38,030
Fate,

504
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:39,960
thank you,

505
00:21:40,200 --> 00:21:42,200
for giving me a chance to start over.

506
00:21:48,470 --> 00:21:49,470
And thank you too.

507
00:21:52,840 --> 00:21:53,710
The truth is,

508
00:21:54,510 --> 00:21:55,350
I can't

509
00:21:55,350 --> 00:21:56,590
keep denying that,

510
00:21:57,480 --> 00:21:59,810
without even realizing it, I have already

511
00:21:59,960 --> 00:22:01,030
been moved by him.

512
00:22:04,270 --> 00:22:05,720
If someone loves you,

513
00:22:06,360 --> 00:22:07,160
respects you,

514
00:22:07,720 --> 00:22:08,720
and protects you,

515
00:22:09,240 --> 00:22:11,110
who cares if it's a dream?

516
00:22:13,510 --> 00:22:14,170
Zhou Cheng.

517
00:22:16,480 --> 00:22:17,010
Xiaolan.

518
00:22:19,200 --> 00:22:19,880
Actually, I don't have

519
00:22:19,880 --> 00:22:21,280
much dating experience,

520
00:22:22,790 --> 00:22:24,200
and I never imagined

521
00:22:24,880 --> 00:22:26,340
I'd meet someone like you.

522
00:22:27,350 --> 00:22:28,810
But I promise, from now on,

523
00:22:29,510 --> 00:22:30,910
I won't run away anymore.

524
00:22:32,150 --> 00:22:33,100
So,

525
00:22:35,550 --> 00:22:37,160
should we give this a try?

526
00:22:42,830 --> 00:22:43,200
I...

527
00:22:43,200 --> 00:22:43,660
I agree.

528
00:22:54,460 --> 00:22:57,760
♪ I don't know when it started ♪

529
00:22:56,920 --> 00:22:57,920
Comrade Xiaolan,

530
00:22:58,200 --> 00:23:01,610
♪ But my world suddenly became bright ♪

531
00:22:59,440 --> 00:23:00,440
I will definitely

532
00:23:00,790 --> 00:23:01,720
take our relationship seriously.

533
00:23:01,630 --> 00:23:05,150
♪ In the second our eyes met ♪

534
00:23:04,200 --> 00:23:04,590
Okay.

535
00:23:06,490 --> 00:23:09,110
♪ I knew it had to be you ♪

536
00:23:07,790 --> 00:23:08,680
Well then,

537
00:23:09,790 --> 00:23:11,450
from now on, call me "Beauty."

538
00:23:15,480 --> 00:23:15,940
Beauty.

539
00:23:18,160 --> 00:23:18,680
Beauty.

540
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:30,810
Xia Changzheng,

541
00:23:31,400 --> 00:23:33,000
I've asked you several times already.

542
00:23:33,000 --> 00:23:35,000
Why did Zhao Gang
and Zhao Yong attack you?

543
00:23:35,000 --> 00:23:35,930
Where's my hand?

544
00:23:36,750 --> 00:23:37,680
Where's my hand?

545
00:23:38,750 --> 00:23:39,680
Where's my hand?

546
00:23:40,450 --> 00:23:41,920
Calm down, Xia Changzheng.

547
00:23:41,920 --> 00:23:43,520
I can't live without my hand!

548
00:23:43,680 --> 00:23:45,600
My hand... My hand...

549
00:23:47,510 --> 00:23:48,480
My hand...

550
00:23:49,640 --> 00:23:50,070
My...

551
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:51,880
Last night,

552
00:23:52,070 --> 00:23:53,870
Freckles Sun turned himself in.

553
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:54,550
He said

554
00:23:55,030 --> 00:23:56,920
Xia Changzheng instigated him

555
00:23:57,590 --> 00:23:59,520
to come to your school and hurt you.

556
00:24:00,110 --> 00:24:02,750
The goal was to stop you from taking
the college entrance exam.

557
00:24:02,750 --> 00:24:04,350
Why did he suddenly confess?

558
00:24:05,750 --> 00:24:06,350
He said

559
00:24:06,960 --> 00:24:07,920
that now the whole village

560
00:24:07,920 --> 00:24:09,510
is talking about you every day.

561
00:24:09,510 --> 00:24:10,910
And after he saw you on TV,

562
00:24:11,200 --> 00:24:13,060
he thought you had become famous.

563
00:24:13,350 --> 00:24:15,280
No matter what you tell the police,

564
00:24:15,480 --> 00:24:16,810
we'd believe it anyway.

565
00:24:16,880 --> 00:24:18,310
Rather than staying at home
waiting to be caught,

566
00:24:18,310 --> 00:24:19,720
he thought it would be better
to turn himself in.

567
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:21,160
The police rely on evidence.

568
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:22,590
Although Xiaolan is famous now,

569
00:24:22,590 --> 00:24:24,520
it wouldn't affect your judgment.

570
00:24:24,920 --> 00:24:26,270
He was guilty

571
00:24:26,590 --> 00:24:28,050
and scared out of his mind.

572
00:24:28,400 --> 00:24:28,960
Later,

573
00:24:29,000 --> 00:24:30,140
we went to Dahe Village

574
00:24:30,140 --> 00:24:32,670
to get more information
from Xia Changzheng,

575
00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:33,740
but he wasn't home.

576
00:24:34,000 --> 00:24:34,640
We eventually

577
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:35,680
found him

578
00:24:35,920 --> 00:24:36,720
in a haystack.

579
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:38,960
His hand had already been cut.

580
00:24:39,500 --> 00:24:40,610
Zhao Yong

581
00:24:40,920 --> 00:24:42,720
and his brother Zhao Gang did it.

582
00:24:43,160 --> 00:24:44,200
Do you know them?

583
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:45,750
Not really.

584
00:24:46,200 --> 00:24:47,160
We have a clothing store

585
00:24:47,160 --> 00:24:48,160
in Shangdu.

586
00:24:48,360 --> 00:24:50,220
They often come to cause trouble.

587
00:24:50,640 --> 00:24:51,640
That makes sense.

588
00:24:51,840 --> 00:24:53,790
He also took money from Xia Changzheng.

589
00:24:53,790 --> 00:24:54,680
It seems that

590
00:24:54,840 --> 00:24:56,970
Xia Changzheng didn't pay them later.

591
00:24:57,310 --> 00:24:59,000
When Zhao Yong learned that Xia Changzheng

592
00:24:59,000 --> 00:25:00,240
had sold the eatery

593
00:25:00,270 --> 00:25:01,160
and made some money,

594
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:02,420
he went to look for him,

595
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:03,000
and

596
00:25:03,110 --> 00:25:04,710
they ended up having a fight.

597
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:07,160
This Xia Changzheng

598
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:08,450
is Xiaolan's uncle.

599
00:25:09,030 --> 00:25:10,160
Why does he keep doing

600
00:25:10,160 --> 00:25:10,960
these things?

601
00:25:11,280 --> 00:25:12,920
It's as if he doesn't want Xiaolan

602
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:14,480
to study and take the exam.

603
00:25:14,880 --> 00:25:16,270
Now I finally know

604
00:25:16,550 --> 00:25:19,150
how the Xia family
has been harming my Xiaolan.

605
00:25:19,550 --> 00:25:20,640
I really regret

606
00:25:21,070 --> 00:25:22,830
being so blind for all these years.

607
00:25:22,830 --> 00:25:24,640
I should have left that family long ago.

608
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:25,030
Mom,

609
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:27,830
this matter is far beyond

610
00:25:27,830 --> 00:25:29,430
a simple family dispute now.

611
00:25:30,240 --> 00:25:31,160
The police

612
00:25:31,180 --> 00:25:32,440
will give us an answer.

613
00:25:32,960 --> 00:25:34,960
I just don't understand.

614
00:25:35,590 --> 00:25:36,960
When I transferred

615
00:25:37,070 --> 00:25:38,510
to Anqing No.1 High School,

616
00:25:38,510 --> 00:25:41,110
my parents had already been separated
for a long time,

617
00:25:41,110 --> 00:25:42,310
and I never spent a cent

618
00:25:42,310 --> 00:25:43,790
of my uncle's family's money
on my studies.

619
00:25:43,790 --> 00:25:45,400
Why would they try so hard to hurt me

620
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:48,070
and stop me
from taking the college entrance exam?

621
00:25:48,070 --> 00:25:49,110
What motive

622
00:25:49,110 --> 00:25:50,570
could they possibly have?

623
00:25:50,790 --> 00:25:51,920
We want to

624
00:25:51,920 --> 00:25:52,790
know that too.

625
00:25:53,400 --> 00:25:53,960
But

626
00:25:54,310 --> 00:25:56,400
given Xia Changzheng's current condition,

627
00:25:56,400 --> 00:25:57,830
he can't confess anything.

628
00:25:57,830 --> 00:25:58,480
We'll

629
00:25:58,480 --> 00:25:59,940
continue investigating.

630
00:26:01,310 --> 00:26:02,550
Where is my aunt?

631
00:26:03,070 --> 00:26:04,550
You mean Xia Changzheng's wife,

632
00:26:04,550 --> 00:26:05,150
Zhang Cui?

633
00:26:05,350 --> 00:26:05,750
Yes.

634
00:26:06,110 --> 00:26:07,200
When we arrived at their house,

635
00:26:07,200 --> 00:26:07,960
she had already fainted.

636
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:09,260
I think it was from shock.

637
00:26:09,260 --> 00:26:09,880
Right now she's

638
00:26:09,880 --> 00:26:11,140
lying in bed next door.

639
00:26:12,680 --> 00:26:13,880
This is Officer Zhao.

640
00:26:14,270 --> 00:26:15,400
He'll stay in touch with you

641
00:26:15,400 --> 00:26:16,680
about the follow-up.

642
00:26:18,030 --> 00:26:18,440
That's it for now.

643
00:26:18,440 --> 00:26:18,790
Okay.

644
00:26:19,240 --> 00:26:19,640
Okay.

645
00:26:20,310 --> 00:26:21,200
Thank you, sirs.

646
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:21,860
No problem.

647
00:26:24,160 --> 00:26:26,270
Did you see my cousin?

648
00:26:26,750 --> 00:26:27,750
You have a cousin?

649
00:26:28,310 --> 00:26:28,640
Yes.

650
00:26:28,880 --> 00:26:30,010
Her name is Xia Ziyu.

651
00:26:30,070 --> 00:26:31,510
She studies at a university in Jingcheng

652
00:26:31,510 --> 00:26:33,710
and has already come home for vacation.

653
00:26:34,590 --> 00:26:35,480
I remember

654
00:26:35,790 --> 00:26:37,510
she came to school to find me

655
00:26:37,720 --> 00:26:39,640
on the day when the results came out.

656
00:26:39,640 --> 00:26:40,500
And what did she

657
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:41,700
say to you that day?

658
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:48,970
Xia Xiaolan,

659
00:26:49,590 --> 00:26:51,850
you just have to go against me, don't you?

660
00:26:53,480 --> 00:26:54,200
Xia Ziyu,

661
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:56,270
listen to yourself.

662
00:26:57,350 --> 00:26:59,400
Everyone
can take the college entrance exam.

663
00:26:59,400 --> 00:27:01,130
I got into university on my own.

664
00:27:01,310 --> 00:27:02,970
How is that going against you?

665
00:27:03,640 --> 00:27:05,070
I like Wang Jianhua,

666
00:27:05,640 --> 00:27:07,240
but you had to steal him away.

667
00:27:08,070 --> 00:27:08,880
I got into college

668
00:27:08,880 --> 00:27:10,110
and left that lousy place,

669
00:27:10,110 --> 00:27:11,240
and you had to follow me.

670
00:27:11,240 --> 00:27:13,440
You compete with me for everything I do.

671
00:27:13,480 --> 00:27:14,210
Xia Xiaolan,

672
00:27:15,000 --> 00:27:15,960
why?

673
00:27:19,160 --> 00:27:19,960
Xia Ziyu,

674
00:27:21,270 --> 00:27:23,070
you've really disappointed me.

675
00:27:23,550 --> 00:27:24,680
I thought

676
00:27:25,350 --> 00:27:26,270
I was dealing with

677
00:27:26,270 --> 00:27:27,270
a smart opponent.

678
00:27:28,160 --> 00:27:28,550
I didn't expect you

679
00:27:28,550 --> 00:27:29,920
to be this foolish.

680
00:27:30,510 --> 00:27:31,200
Shut up.

681
00:27:32,510 --> 00:27:33,240
You think

682
00:27:33,440 --> 00:27:35,230
just because you have good grades

683
00:27:35,230 --> 00:27:37,270
and pretend to be obedient
and well‑behaved,

684
00:27:37,270 --> 00:27:39,470
the whole world should make way for you?

685
00:27:39,750 --> 00:27:40,510
Xia Ziyu,

686
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:42,740
where do you get such confidence?

687
00:27:43,030 --> 00:27:44,830
I didn't compete with you before

688
00:27:45,030 --> 00:27:46,830
because I couldn't be bothered.

689
00:27:47,110 --> 00:27:48,440
The things you treasure

690
00:27:48,440 --> 00:27:50,000
are worthless

691
00:27:50,310 --> 00:27:51,510
to me.

692
00:27:53,030 --> 00:27:54,760
Wang Jianhua? Someone like him

693
00:27:55,240 --> 00:27:57,030
would throw himself at me

694
00:27:57,310 --> 00:27:59,170
without me even lifting a finger.

695
00:28:00,310 --> 00:28:01,110
Xia Ziyu,

696
00:28:02,000 --> 00:28:04,200
maybe you should take a good look
in the mirror

697
00:28:04,200 --> 00:28:06,550
and see how useless you really are.

698
00:28:12,310 --> 00:28:13,790
So you've finally decided to act yourself,

699
00:28:13,790 --> 00:28:14,520
haven't you?

700
00:28:16,350 --> 00:28:17,680
Put away your weakness.

701
00:28:18,240 --> 00:28:19,770
That trick won't work on me.

702
00:28:20,150 --> 00:28:21,510
Show your fangs,

703
00:28:21,510 --> 00:28:23,640
and I might respect you as an opponent.

704
00:28:24,400 --> 00:28:25,110
Xia Ziyu,

705
00:28:25,830 --> 00:28:27,360
I'll tell you one last time—

706
00:28:28,190 --> 00:28:29,950
I never hurt people first,

707
00:28:31,640 --> 00:28:33,720
but if you keep provoking me,

708
00:28:34,240 --> 00:28:35,500
I will never back down.

709
00:28:36,160 --> 00:28:38,290
Whoever made trouble at Blue Phoenix,

710
00:28:38,960 --> 00:28:40,680
whoever spread rumors about me,

711
00:28:40,680 --> 00:28:42,240
and whoever stepped on my wrist—

712
00:28:42,240 --> 00:28:43,750
I won't let any of them off.

713
00:28:44,460 --> 00:28:46,060
And I definitely won't spare

714
00:28:46,710 --> 00:28:49,170
the person pulling the strings
behind them.

715
00:28:57,880 --> 00:28:58,480
Ziyu,

716
00:28:59,200 --> 00:29:00,160
this is the letter of introduction

717
00:29:00,160 --> 00:29:01,160
you asked me to write—

718
00:29:01,160 --> 00:29:02,490
without a destination.

719
00:29:04,510 --> 00:29:06,090
Where are you going that you need

720
00:29:06,090 --> 00:29:08,240
[Letter of Introduction]

721
00:29:06,310 --> 00:29:09,040
a letter of introduction
without a destination?

722
00:29:11,160 --> 00:29:12,350
This is yours. And this is yours.

723
00:29:12,350 --> 00:29:13,680
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

724
00:29:13,900 --> 00:29:14,620
Come often.

725
00:29:14,830 --> 00:29:15,480
Take care.

726
00:29:21,350 --> 00:29:22,350
Fen! Fen!

727
00:29:22,920 --> 00:29:23,650
Look at this!

728
00:29:23,790 --> 00:29:24,440
What?

729
00:29:25,270 --> 00:29:26,350
Look who this is.

730
00:29:27,270 --> 00:29:28,480
Xia Ziyu!

731
00:29:28,060 --> 00:29:30,380
[Case of Top Science Scorer in Yunan Province
Being Attacked Solved Today]

732
00:29:29,140 --> 00:29:30,000
Oh my goodness.

733
00:29:30,000 --> 00:29:31,270
Ziyu's a fugitive now?

734
00:29:34,000 --> 00:29:35,880
The day the police came to our house,

735
00:29:35,880 --> 00:29:37,720
my legs nearly gave out from fear.

736
00:29:37,720 --> 00:29:39,160
That was because of Ziyu?

737
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:40,480
Isn't it written clearly

738
00:29:40,480 --> 00:29:41,560
in the newspaper?

739
00:29:41,750 --> 00:29:44,210
Xia Ziyu is the mastermind.
The mastermind!

740
00:29:44,640 --> 00:29:45,880
I heard she ran off
with a fake letter of introduction

741
00:29:45,880 --> 00:29:47,340
Wang Jianhua made for her.

742
00:29:47,640 --> 00:29:48,160
Look.

743
00:29:48,440 --> 00:29:49,400
She incited Zhang Erlai

744
00:29:49,400 --> 00:29:50,530
to bully our Xiaolan

745
00:29:50,680 --> 00:29:52,240
and ordered someone to hurt Xiaolan.

746
00:29:52,240 --> 00:29:53,270
With all these charges,

747
00:29:53,270 --> 00:29:55,000
she's going to prison for sure.

748
00:29:55,270 --> 00:29:56,480
This is truly wicked,

749
00:29:56,480 --> 00:29:57,330
doing such things.

750
00:29:57,330 --> 00:29:58,930
Her father was arrested too?

751
00:29:59,030 --> 00:29:59,790
So does that mean no one will

752
00:29:59,790 --> 00:30:01,790
cause trouble for Xiaolan anymore?

753
00:30:01,960 --> 00:30:04,030
Look at what happened to these people.

754
00:30:04,030 --> 00:30:05,070
They wouldn't dare

755
00:30:05,070 --> 00:30:06,130
in a million years.

756
00:30:08,030 --> 00:30:08,400
Mom.

757
00:30:08,400 --> 00:30:08,920
Fen, do you think...

758
00:30:08,920 --> 00:30:09,400
Auntie.

759
00:30:11,920 --> 00:30:12,920
What are you talking about?

760
00:30:12,920 --> 00:30:13,750
Nothing.

761
00:30:13,750 --> 00:30:14,880
N-nothing, really.

762
00:30:15,160 --> 00:30:16,200
N-nothing.

763
00:30:16,640 --> 00:30:17,500
Stop hiding it.

764
00:30:18,270 --> 00:30:18,830
Auntie.

765
00:30:20,680 --> 00:30:21,210
Alright.

766
00:30:21,450 --> 00:30:22,840
I won't pretend with you anymore.

767
00:30:22,840 --> 00:30:23,310
Look.

768
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:24,680
Xia Ziyu.

769
00:30:27,640 --> 00:30:28,640
Tell me the truth.

770
00:30:29,590 --> 00:30:30,680
Was Xia Ziyu getting arrested

771
00:30:30,680 --> 00:30:31,920
part of your plan?

772
00:30:33,180 --> 00:30:34,550
And that Huang's Rice Bowl place

773
00:30:34,550 --> 00:30:35,550
next to the school—

774
00:30:35,550 --> 00:30:37,750
were you the one who gave them that idea?

775
00:30:37,750 --> 00:30:39,010
And the Zhao brothers—

776
00:30:39,110 --> 00:30:39,920
how did they know

777
00:30:39,920 --> 00:30:41,240
Xia Changzheng had money

778
00:30:41,240 --> 00:30:42,960
after selling the eatery?

779
00:30:43,960 --> 00:30:44,630
Auntie.

780
00:30:45,030 --> 00:30:46,200
I should open

781
00:30:46,200 --> 00:30:46,880
a detective agency for you

782
00:30:46,880 --> 00:30:48,350
next door.

783
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:50,160
Really?

784
00:30:50,160 --> 00:30:51,450
So I was right?

785
00:30:51,480 --> 00:30:52,480
Detective?

786
00:30:52,480 --> 00:30:53,440
Everything your auntie just said

787
00:30:53,440 --> 00:30:54,310
is true?

788
00:30:55,290 --> 00:30:57,160
Whether it's true or not
doesn't matter anymore.

789
00:30:57,160 --> 00:30:58,400
Hurry and eat this beef

790
00:30:58,400 --> 00:30:59,960
I stewed for 3 hours.

791
00:31:00,270 --> 00:31:01,750
Hot, hot, hot. Hurry.

792
00:31:03,270 --> 00:31:03,800
Xiaolan,

793
00:31:04,310 --> 00:31:05,170
what are these?

794
00:31:05,480 --> 00:31:06,110
Mr. Sun,

795
00:31:06,310 --> 00:31:07,720
these are my study materials

796
00:31:07,720 --> 00:31:09,160
from when I was reviewing.

797
00:31:09,160 --> 00:31:10,760
There are some notes I wrote.

798
00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:11,680
And this one

799
00:31:11,680 --> 00:31:12,920
contains my study methods.

800
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:13,640
Maybe

801
00:31:13,640 --> 00:31:15,100
they can help the juniors.

802
00:31:15,420 --> 00:31:16,480
Great. Have a seat.

803
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:16,880
Okay.

804
00:31:18,960 --> 00:31:19,490
Xiaolan.

805
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:21,530
Is your hand still hurting?

806
00:31:21,550 --> 00:31:23,150
It stopped hurting long ago.

807
00:31:24,110 --> 00:31:25,240
You are

808
00:31:25,550 --> 00:31:26,790
such a proud child.

809
00:31:27,030 --> 00:31:27,860
I know

810
00:31:28,020 --> 00:31:29,880
you've been through a lot before,

811
00:31:30,160 --> 00:31:31,760
and life hasn't been easy for you.

812
00:31:31,760 --> 00:31:33,550
But now you've made it out

813
00:31:33,790 --> 00:31:35,190
through your own effort—

814
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:37,260
you never have to look back again.

815
00:31:37,320 --> 00:31:38,590
You're a smart child,

816
00:31:38,590 --> 00:31:40,050
so I don't need to say much.

817
00:31:40,960 --> 00:31:41,760
I just wish you

818
00:31:42,310 --> 00:31:43,350
a bright future

819
00:31:43,790 --> 00:31:45,050
and a proud path ahead.

820
00:31:46,820 --> 00:31:47,880
Thank you, Mr. Sun.

821
00:31:49,790 --> 00:31:50,720
Xia Xiaolan!

822
00:31:51,480 --> 00:31:52,480
Registered mail!

823
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:55,160
Xia Xiaolan!

824
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:56,640
Registered mail!

825
00:31:58,070 --> 00:31:58,960
Xia Xiaolan!

826
00:31:59,440 --> 00:32:00,440
Registered mail!

827
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:01,160
Slow down!

828
00:32:02,890 --> 00:32:04,410
It's coming! Hurry!

829
00:32:04,440 --> 00:32:05,200
Hurry up!

830
00:32:05,920 --> 00:32:06,640
Thank you!

831
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:07,450
Our boss said

832
00:32:07,550 --> 00:32:09,000
your family has been asking every day.

833
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:09,920
When he saw this,

834
00:32:09,920 --> 00:32:10,550
he told me

835
00:32:10,550 --> 00:32:11,440
to deliver it to you right away.

836
00:32:11,440 --> 00:32:12,770
Your admission letter.

837
00:32:12,830 --> 00:32:14,630
Congratulations, Xia Xiaolan.

838
00:32:16,230 --> 00:32:17,440
Mom, you take it.

839
00:32:20,920 --> 00:32:22,550
Hurry, Fen!

840
00:32:25,820 --> 00:32:26,470
Thank you.

841
00:32:26,740 --> 00:32:27,160
You're welcome.

842
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:28,240
Fen, open it.

843
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:29,170
Open it already!

844
00:32:35,680 --> 00:32:38,270
Huaqing University Admission Letter.

845
00:32:38,720 --> 00:32:39,960
Ms. Xiaolan,

846
00:32:40,400 --> 00:32:41,350
you have been approved

847
00:32:41,350 --> 00:32:43,280
for admission to our university's

848
00:32:43,400 --> 00:32:45,400
School of Architecture,
Department of Architecture,

849
00:32:45,400 --> 00:32:47,590
majoring in Architecture.

850
00:32:47,920 --> 00:32:49,920
Please register with this letter

851
00:32:49,920 --> 00:32:52,240
between September 1st

852
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:55,030
and 10th, 1984.

853
00:32:55,790 --> 00:32:56,750
Bravo!

854
00:33:50,030 --> 00:33:50,920
The 1984

855
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:52,270
Mathematics college entrance exam

856
00:33:52,270 --> 00:33:53,200
begins now.

857
00:33:56,350 --> 00:33:57,750
Why is math so difficult?

858
00:33:59,350 --> 00:34:00,110
Everything seems

859
00:34:00,110 --> 00:34:01,910
to be going according to my plan,

860
00:34:02,440 --> 00:34:03,750
but only I know

861
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:05,550
that this math paper

862
00:34:06,030 --> 00:34:08,760
is completely different
from the one I remember.

863
00:34:10,670 --> 00:34:12,480
It feels like a reminder

864
00:34:13,320 --> 00:34:14,510
that everything now

865
00:34:14,920 --> 00:34:16,449
isn't as real as it appears.

866
00:34:17,400 --> 00:34:19,000
I don't know if these changes

867
00:34:19,280 --> 00:34:20,150
will alter

868
00:34:20,150 --> 00:34:21,480
this chapter of my life.

869
00:34:57,870 --> 00:34:59,010
[Admission Letter of Huaqing University]

870
00:35:15,670 --> 00:35:16,110
Fen,

871
00:35:16,590 --> 00:35:17,710
you even pulled out

872
00:35:17,710 --> 00:35:18,960
all of Xiaolan's winter clothes?

873
00:35:18,960 --> 00:35:20,150
Haven't they been stored for a year?

874
00:35:20,150 --> 00:35:20,920
So I'm airing them out

875
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:22,480
so she can take them when she leaves.

876
00:35:22,480 --> 00:35:22,880
Look.

877
00:35:23,480 --> 00:35:24,400
This is

878
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:26,110
the new cotton quilt I made for her.

879
00:35:26,110 --> 00:35:27,240
I'll let her take it.

